      "content": "Thanks, those are some solid pillars for them to build on. Now, for the second half of their prep, they need to be ready for the rebuttals. What would be the strongest, most sophisticated arguments the opposition would use against this position? I want them to be able to handle the high-level philosophical and humanitarian critiques, not just the basic ones.",
